{
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "text": "%md\n# рџ›ЎпёЏ Fine-Tune MiniFASNet v2 вЂ” Multi-Source Anti-Spoofing\n\n**Mб»Ґc tiГЄu:** Fine-tune MiniFASNet trГЄn **nhiб»Ѓu dataset kбєїt hб»Јp** Д‘б»ѓ model khГґng overfit theo 1 camera/ГЎnh sГЎng.\n\n| ThГґng sб»‘ | GiГЎ trб»‹ |\n|---|---|\n| Model | MiniFASNetV2 (MobileNetV2 backbone, ~2.2M params) |\n| Input | `(B, 3, 128, 128)` RGB normalized `[0,1]` |\n| Output | `(B, 2)` logits `[real_logit, spoof_logit]` |\n| Datasets | OULU-NPU + Replay-Attack + CASIA-FASD + AxonData + Custom |\n| Platform | Apache Zeppelin (Windows, GPU) |\n\n### TбєЎi sao phбєЈi Multi-Source?\n\n| CГЎch train | Kбєїt quбєЈ |\n|---|---|\n| 1 dataset | Hб»Ќc thuб»™c camera/ГЎnh sГЎng dataset Д‘Гі в†’ fail ngoГ i Д‘б»ќi |\n| Multi-dataset + domain shuffle | Hiб»ѓu bбєЈn chбєҐt texture giбєЈ в†’ hoбєЎt Д‘б»™ng б»џ mб»Ќi mГґi trЖ°б»ќng |",
